 crazy, idk what to believe on this. The bitch goes to Italy without telling anyone, prior to the attack. Same bitch who announces when her shit is green, somehow \"forgets\" (her own claim) to tell her audience about the trip. \r\nAnyhow, prior to the attack, Google trend data showed that there was a search for Cole Allen, coming out of Italy. \r\nAside from a few posts, she's basically gone dark. No podcasts, no comments in the attack, only \"Sorry, guess I forgot to tell you guys about my family trip\" or some shit like that. \r\nI don't get into every rabbit hole, but I despise this insufferable bitch. \r\nhttps://x.com/i/status/2048758791026413860\r\n\r\nOr maybe Cole is trans and Candace is him in drag. \ud83d\ude02", "author": "Firespawn", "created": 1777462676142, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "mojorisen", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Candace Owens ties to Cole Allen? ", "last_comment_created": 1777481299386, "content": "<p>It's crazy, idk what to believe on this. The bitch goes to Italy without telling anyone, prior to the attack. Same bitch who announces when her shit is green, somehow &quot;forgets&quot; (her own claim) to tell her audience about the trip.\nAnyhow, prior to the attack, Google trend data showed that there was a search for Cole Allen, coming out of Italy.\nAside from a few posts, she's basically gone dark. No podcasts, no comments in the attack, only &quot;Sorry, guess I forgot to tell you guys about my family trip&quot; or some shit like that.\nI don't get into every rabbit hole, but I despise this insufferable bitch.\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://x.com/i/status/2048758791026413860\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/i/status/204875879